    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. u mentioned the costs and compliance issues, but what about the actual intent behind them? some people in our district are saying the environmental benefits are pretty much unproven or just theoretical compared to the real-world loss of jobs. do u have any info on whether those benefits actually balance out the economic hit?",
